CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,FThe mother of missing Ben Needham has
OL,7,Fcalled on the UK Government to "take
OL,8,Fresponsibility" and back her
OL,9,Fdiplomatic fight with the Greek
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FBen, from Sheffield, vanished on the
OL,13,Fisland of Kos on 24 July 1991 at the
OL,14,Fage of 21 months.
OL,16,FSpeaking ahead of the 35th anniversary
OL,17,Fof her son's disappearance, Kerry
OL,18,FNeedham said "no-one's listening" to
OL,19,Fher plight in Greece and called for
OL,20,Fgovernment help.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,F"They can't sit back any longer, watch
OL,7,Fme suffer, and not do anything about
OL,8,Fit," she said.
OL,10,F"Ben is a British child. Yes, we were
OL,11,Fon the island of Kos. (But) he holds a
OL,12,FBritish passport, I hold a British
OL,13,Fpassport. The UK government have to
OL,14,Ftake some responsibility to back me in
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,26,@sD@WpmsD@[pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,F"I'm a mother trying to fight this
OL,7,Fbattle alone, and I will continue to
OL,8,Fdo so. So if anybody thinks, oh well,
OL,9,Fit's been 35 years, she'll go away
OL,10,Feventually, they're very, very wrong,
OL,11,Fbecause I won't."
OL,13,FDespite more than #1million being
OL,14,Fspent on the investigation - including
OL,15,Ftwo excavations at the farmhouse where
OL,16,FBen was last seen - his whereabouts
OL,17,Fremain unknown.
OL,19,FKerry met with Foreign Office
OL,20,Fofficials in a bid to open diplomatic
OL,21,Fchannels with Greece.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,FShe continued: "I have begged, I have
OL,7,Fpleaded, I have cried, I have broken
OL,8,Fdown on Greek TV. No one's listening
OL,9,Fto me over there."
OL,11,F"It has to come now from a government
OL,12,Flevel."
OL,14,FOliver Coppard, Mayor for South
OL,15,FYorkshire, helped Kerry secure the
OL,16,Fministerial meeting and his backing
OL,17,Fher campaign for more support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,FHe said: "She absolutely needs to do
OL,7,Feverything in her power to be able to
OL,8,Fmake people sit up and listen. And I
OL,9,Fam there alongside her, helping her to
OL,10,Fdo just that.
OL,12,F"She needs all the support that she
OL,13,Fcan get from the state, from the
OL,14,Fsystem, to make sure that she's not
OL,15,Fhaving to work out exactly where to go
OL,16,Fnext.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,F"That means working with the
OL,7,Fgovernment`whoever the government may
OL,8,Fbe`to make sure that they're doing
OL,9,Feverything they can with their Greek
OL,10,Fcounterparts."
OL,12,FReflecting on the anniversary, Kerry
OL,13,Fsaid: "I think 35 years is a massive
OL,14,Fmilestone. I was a very young mother
OL,15,Fat the time.
OL,17,F"These people who, whatever happened
OL,18,Fto Ben, and who was responsible for
OL,19,Fwhat happened to Ben, nothing is going
OL,20,Fto happen to them.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,F"So I need justice in another way. I
OL,7,Fneed to know them answers.
OL,9,F"And every time another anniversary
OL,10,Fcomes along, it brings me back to the
OL,11,Fday that he disappeared, when someone
OL,12,Fdid something to my son."
OL,14,FIn a statement, South Yorkshire Police
OL,15,Fsaid their thoughts were with Ben's
OL,16,Ffamily and called for anyone with
OL,17,Finformation to come forward.
OL,19,F"It's never too late to share
OL,20,Finformation with us," they said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784917111
OL,3,CMissing boy's mum demands government
OL,4,Cintervention 35 years on
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Foreign,
OL,7,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,8,Fconfirmed minister Stephen Doughty met
OL,9,FKerry and added: "Our thoughts are
OL,10,Fwith the family of Ben Needham on the
OL,11,Fanniversary of his disappearance."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
